    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基批评西方盟友在俄罗斯向库尔斯克附近推进时迟迟不提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/zelenskiy-blasts-western-allies-for-slow-aid-amid-russian-push-near-kursk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰领导人加大对西方伙伴支持力度不足的批评，同时声称乌克兰军队从上个月开始入侵俄罗斯，减缓了莫斯科在其他前线的进攻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/zelenskiy-blasts-western-allies-for-slow-aid-amid-russian-push-near-kursk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 13:46:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望对美元叛逃者征收巨额关税，减少美国制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/trump-touts-a-mega-tariff-to-shield-dollar-cools-on-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在其第一任总统任期内开创了使用关税作为治国武器的新方法。他承诺下次将全力以赴——甚至部署一个巨型版本来保护美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/trump-touts-a-mega-tariff-to-shield-dollar-cools-on-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
